Prerequisites 
  
  * Sjsws 7.0 update 5 installed
  
  * Java jre 1.6 installed
  
  * The file /opt/BBS/Software/\<version\>/\<date\>/ts_idp_nemid/ts_idp_nemid-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT.war
  
  * The file /opt/BBS/Software/\<version\>/\<date\>/ts_idp_nemid/ts_idp_nemid-config-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT-\<env\>.zip
  
  * An utterly large amount of edb karma combined with a rediculous high computer mojo factor


