Installation

* Installation overview
The installation should take approximately 10 minutes

* Pre installation steps
  
*-----------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|<<description>>                    |<<requirement>>                                                                                                                      |<<comment>>           |<<branch 1>>|<<branch 2>>|<<branch 3>>|<<branch 4>>|
*-----------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Copy release to target machine     |# scp ts_idp_nemid-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT.war root@\<global zone\>:/opt/BBS/Software/\<version\>/\<date\>/ts_idp_nemid/                |                      |            |            |            |            |
*-----------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Copy config to target machine      |# scp ts_idp_nemid-config-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT-\<env\>.zip root@\<global zone\>:/opt/BBS/Software/\<version\>/\<date\>/ts_idp_nemid/ |                      |            |            |            |            |
*-----------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|...                                |...                                                                                                                                  |...                   |            |            |            |            |
*-----------------------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+


* Installation steps

*---------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|<<description>>      |<<requirement>>                                                                                                                                                                                         |<<comment>>           |<<branch 1>>|<<branch 2>>|<<branch 3>>|<<branch 4>>|
*---------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Log into local zone  |# ssh root@\<local zone\>                                                                                                                                                                               |                      |            |            |            |            |
*---------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Unzip properties     |# cd /opt/bbs/properties/ts_idp_nemid                                                                                                                                                         |                      |            |            |            |            | 
|                     |# unzip /opt/BBS/Software/\<version\>/\<date\>/ts_idp_nemid/ts_idp_nemid-config-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT-\<env\>.zip                                                                                        |                      |            |            |            |            |
*---------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Run deploy script    |# /opt/BBS/Software/Deploy/ip7tool.ksh -D -c \<configuration\>  -v \<virtualserver\> -u /ts_idp_nemid -w /opt/BBS/Software/\<version\>/\<date\>/ts_idp_nemid/ts_idp_nemid-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT.war |                      |            |            |            |            |
*---------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+


* Post installation steps
  
*-----------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|<<description>>        |<<requirement>>                                               |<<comment>>           |<<branch 1>>|<<branch 2>>|<<branch 3>>|<<branch 4>>|
*-----------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Restart web server     |# /opt/sun_web/servers/\<instance\>/bin/stopserv              |                      |            |            |            |            |
|                       |# /opt/sun_web/servers/\<instance\>/bin/startserv             |                      |            |            |            |            |
*-----------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Check logs for success |# tail -100f /opt/BBS/logs/maintenance/ts_idp_nemid.log  |                      |            |            |            |            |
*-----------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+


* Rollback procedure in case of installation failure
  
*-----------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- -------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|<<description>>        |<<requirement>>                                                                                                                                                                                                          |<<comment>>           |<<branch 1>>|<<branch 2>>|<<branch 3>>|<<branch 4>>|
*-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Restart web server     |# /opt/sun_web/servers/\<instance\>/bin/stopserv                                                                                                                                                                         |                      |            |            |            |            |       
|                       |# /opt/sun_web/servers/\<instance\>/bin/startserv                                                                                                                                                                         |                      |            |            |            |            |
*-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Run deploy script      |# /opt/BBS/Software/Deploy/ip7tool.ksh -D -c \<configuration\>  -v \<virtualserver\> -u /ts_idp_nemid -w /opt/BBS/Software/\<previous-version\>/\<date\>/ts_idp_nemid/ts_idp_nemid-<previous-version>.war |                      |            |            |            |            |
*-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+
|Check logs for success |# tail -100f /opt/BBS/logs/maintenance/ts_idp_nemid.log                                                                                                                                                             |                      |            |            |            |            |
*-----------------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+----------------------+------------+------------+------------+------------+


